===Etymology===
From [[conifer]] (cone-bearer) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Coniferophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Plantae]] that includes the [[conifer]]s. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

